text: After seeing the reviews below mine, I’m was kinda puzzled about why I was given a free mask when I only bought a drink. Nonetheless, I thank you for the mask. But you really shouldn’t had profiteer from it.  There’s always a time to make $$$ but please don’t forget our morals and ethics we learnt from our parents and school.
Any store that seeks to unscrupulously profiteer from surgical masks in times of uncertain health situation should be avoided and boycotted.
I support you. Government give us 4 lousy mask for every household. What can we do?
